import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import math

num=np.array([])
ratio=np.array([])

for i in range(22,62):
    x=np.linspace(0,8*math.pi,i)
    y=.5*np.sin(x)
    s=np.std(y)
    num=np.append(num,[i])
    ratio=np.append(ratio,[s])

plt.scatter(num,ratio)
